  instructions:
    'Returns vision summaries ordered by createdAt descending (newest first). ' +
    'Filter by stage or codex to narrow results. The default `--format text` ' +
    'renders a tabular view (STAGE | ID | CODEX | TITLE | CREATED) with per-row ' +
