4	 * Single-file test that exercises the full 15-tool matrix through one
5	 * fixture (vision/charge/piece × create/show/list/patch/transition).
6	 * The fixture wires real stacks + real clerk + the cartograph apparatus,
7	 * then dispatches each tool's handler directly through `tool.handler({...})`
8	 * with the params already shaped (skipping the Commander layer that the
9	 * `nsg` auto-builder lives in — that surface is verified separately by
10	 * the framework CLI's own program tests).
11	 *
12	 * Coverage matrix:
13	 *   - Happy paths for every tool (15 × create/show/list/patch/transition).
14	 *   - Parent-id short-prefix resolution on charge-create / piece-create.
15	 *   - Error wrapping for prefix-resolution failures.
16	 *   - Format parity (text vs json) for show and list.
